'''"Shwock Dubllon"''', known as '''"Crested Wake"''' in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], was a piece of classical music by [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] composer [[Dembaline]]. It was considered one of Dembaline's best performances, and was later covered by [[Gaeriel Capens]] using a [[TribBot mimic series]] droid in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

